<br>
* Clerics get a stronger line of spells for dealing with cursed objects, so if you have a cleric and its cursed, get him to deal with it rather than a shaman...<br>
<br>
* Wizards get a stronger line of spells for dealing with magical objects<br>
<br>
* There is currently a bug that means certain people in your group might not be able to loot the object after you have /open 'd it. Apparently if you camp out and back in you will be able to loot. I tried just waiting for 10minutes and that seemed to do the trick too.<br>
<br>
* You can melee a chest to open it if you can't be bothered sensing/disarming/picking. This however has a high chance of destroying a large % of the items inside it.<br>
